==余波==
在最高选举法庭宣布胡安·奥兰多·埃尔南德斯获胜者时，法庭首脑戴维·马塔莫罗斯称，这“不可逆转”（"irreversible"）
，<ref name=irreversible>{{cite web|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/americas/2013/11/polls-close-honduran-election-2013112511524737104.html|title=Hernandez lead 'irreversible' in Honduras|date=November 26, 2013|publisher=[[Al_Jazeera|Al Jazeera]]|accessdate=2013-11-26|archive-date=2020-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200906174535/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/americas/2013/11/polls-close-honduran-election-2013112511524737104.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>但其主要竞选对手、自由和重建党候选人[[希奥玛拉·卡斯特罗·德塞拉亚|希奥玛拉·卡斯特罗·德塞拉亚]]不承认败选，执意要求选举委员会重审计票结果。

卡斯特罗和纳斯拉亚对选举表示异议，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/honduras-election-sparks-protests-competing-claims-of-victory-fraud/2013/11/25/4d15915e-55e1-11e3-bdbf-097ab2a3dc2b_story.html|title=Tension increases in Honduras, as election sparks competing claims of victory, fraud|date=November 25, 2013|publisher=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|accessdate=2013-11-28|archive-date=2020-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200417224931/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/honduras-election-sparks-protests-competing-claims-of-victory-fraud/2013/11/25/4d15915e-55e1-11e3-bdbf-097ab2a3dc2b_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>委内瑞拉总统[[尼古拉斯·马杜罗|尼古拉斯·马杜罗]]也指责美国“干涉洪都拉斯人的内部事务。”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://venezuelanalysis.com/news/10193|title=Venezuela’s Maduro Rejects US "Intervention" in Honduras|date=November 26, 2013|publisher=[[Venezuelanalysis.com|Venezuelanalysis.com]]|accessdate=2013-11-28|archive-date=2013-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131205054749/http://venezuelanalysis.com/news/10193|dead-url=no}}</ref>卡斯特罗则呼吁她的支持者在11月30日周六举行抗议活动。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2013/11/27/world/americas/honduras-presidential-election/|title=Winner named in Honduras presidential vote; opposition vows protests|date=November 27, 2013|publisher=[[CNN|CNN]]|accessdate=2013-11-28|archive-date=2020-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200906180207/https://edition.cnn.com/2013/11/27/world/americas/honduras-presidential-election/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[拉丁美洲北美议会|拉丁美洲北美议会]]称，“选举已经充满了违规行为和暴力恐吓，威胁要把陷入困境的国家带入进一步政治混乱。”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://nacla.org/blog/2013/11/28/honduran-election-results-contested-international-observers|title=Honduran Election Results Contested by International Observers|date=November 28, 2013|publisher=[[North_American_Congress_on_Latin_America|North American Congress on Latin America]]|accessdate=2013-11-28|archive-date=2013-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131214232204/http://nacla.org/blog/2013/11/28/honduran-election-results-contested-international-observers|dead-url=no}}</ref>而[[美洲国家组织|美洲国家组织]]和[[联合国|联合国]]的观察员宣布选举符合国际标准，是自由和公平的。<ref>{{cite web|title=BBC News|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-latin-america-25132240|publisher=BBC|accessdate=7 December 2013|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128112253/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-latin-america-25132240|dead-url=no}}</ref>

